screen_name: I’m remaining abstinent from sex because I love Jesus. And that love that is continuously growing has allowed me to be able to resist even in the midst of temptation. I literally quit cold turkey three years ago and it never became a chore for me to not want to do it. All God.

Found out I tested positive for COVID-19 Wednesday night and for a moment, something strange tried to settle in. 

And then I remembered who I was, and I remembered who HE was, and all the strange thoughts left my head. 

There’s no reason for me to panic.
